The Products module is used to manage all items available in the inventory. It allows administrators or authorized staff to add, edit, delete, and organize product information. Each product record includes details such as the product name, barcode, category, supplier, selling price, cost price, stock quantity, expiration date (if applicable), and product image.
This module helps ensure accurate inventory tracking by monitoring stock levels in real time. It also provides low-stock alerts, making it easier to restock items before they run out. By maintaining complete and organized product information, the Products module improves inventory accuracy, speeds up sales transactions, and supports better business decision-making through reliable product data.
